data.description: Stunning 2019 Granville in CUSD. This 5 bedroom 3 bath Eco Friendly Smart Home with isolated bedroom and bath downstairs boasts quartz counters, large kitchen island, high ceilings, relaxing patio area, and a workshop/shed with electricity in the back yard.This beautiful home is located in a cul-de-sac with easy walk thru access to the neighborhood park and NO HOA. You do not want to miss this one! Schedule your private showing today.
